<% title "Account Sign In" %>

<div style="margin: auto; width: 960;">

  <p>When you first registered we sent you a welcome email with your
  <strong><%= AppConfig.title %></strong> URL.</p>

  <p>If you remember the company name (possible abbreviated) you may enter it here:</p>

  <div class="mock_address_bar">
    <div>
    http://<input id="subdomain" type="text" placeholder="yourcompanyname" />.<%= AppConfig.domain %>
    </div>
    <input type="button" value="Go" onclick="javascript: try_url();" />
  </div>

  <p>You need to go to this address to login.</p>
  <p>If can&apos;t remember the company name and you&apos;ve lost the welcome email, just send an
  email to <%= mail_to AppConfig.support_email %> and we&apos;ll help you figure out your URL.</p>

</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
  function try_url() {
    var subdomain = $('#subdomain').val();
    if (subdomain=="") {
      alert('Please supply your company name.')
      $('#subdomain').focus();
    } else {
      window.location = 'http://' + subdomain + '.<%= AppConfig.domain %>';
    }
  }
</script>

